title: Ocean Thermal Energy Conversion (OTEC) - Sea Surface Temperature (Annual Average)
name: ocean-thermal-energy-conversion-otec-sea-surface-temperature-annual-average-01a86
notes: This shapefile represents annual average sea surface temperature recordings.rnrnThe sea surface temperature is the temperature of the warm water source used by an OTEC plant.
